text: Hüttwilersee is a lake in the Canton of Thurgau, Switzerland. It is located near two other lakes, Nussbaumersee and Hasensee, on the border of the municipalities of Hüttwilen und Uesslingen-Buch. ==See also== *List of lakes of Switzerland == External links == * Stiftung Seebachtal * Category:Lakes of Thurgau Category:Lakes of Switzerland LHuttwilersee
title: Hüttwilersee
